Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:08.42,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Ano hana kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.13,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}saita no wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.31,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}soko ni tane ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:21.31,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ochita kara de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:26.94,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Itsuka mata kareta ato de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:34.16,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}tane ni natte sidzuiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:43.12,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Kouya o kakeru, kono ryouashi de (going going) sore dake nanda
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:50.71,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Asu e tabidatsu jumbi wa ii kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:57.47,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Soko de tomadou, demo unmei ga (calling calling) yondeiru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:01.68,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}naraba subete o ikitte yare
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:08.19,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Nankai datte yuu yo, sekai wa utsukushii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:16.62,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}kimi ga sore o akiramenai kara dayo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:23.83,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Saishuukai no story wa hajime kara kimateita to shitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:31.09,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ima dake wa koko ni aru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:35.72,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}kimi no mama hikatte yuke yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:08.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Sesuatu yang mekar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}dari bunga itu adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}sebuah biji
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:21.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}yang jatuh ke tanah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:26.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Suatu saat nanti, tanaman yang kering
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:34.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}meninggalkan biji dan menjadi keturunan baru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:43.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Kulalui tanah gersang dengan kedua kakiku ini
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:50.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Apa kau sudah siap untuk perjalanan besok pagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:57.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Sedikit rasa ragu, namun takdir seolah memanggilku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:01.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Maka hiduplah dengan apa yang kaupunya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:08.19,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Kuulangi berulang kali, dunia ini memanglah indah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:16.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}karena dirimu tidak menyerah padanya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:23.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Meski kisahku telah ditetapkan sejak awal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:31.09,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}tapi aku masih di sini, detik ini
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:35.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Maka bersinarlah seperti yang kaumau
